# Account Settings вЂ” Enterprise Architecture Plan

> **Scope:** Maps the enterprise Account Settings specification against our existing platform.
> **Current phase:** Phase 5 complete. Phase 6 (Analytics) is next.
> **Account Settings fits as:** Phase 7.5 (settings required before Phase 8 admin work) 
> Split into 3 sub-phases: **8A (Core Settings)**, **8B (Security & Compliance)**, **8C (Sender Identity)**

