## Section 1 вЂ” Personal Profile

> A user's personal identity layer. Decoupled from the Tenant (org).

| Feature | Priority | What To Build | Already Have? |
|---|---|---|---|
| First name / Last name edit | рџ”ө P0 | PATCH `/auth/me` + profile page UI | No вЂ” only at signup |
| Primary email change (with re-verification loop) | рџџҰ P1 | Email change endpoint + verification email | No |
| Profile avatar upload | рџџұ P2 | Upload to Supabase Storage + CDN link | No |
| Local timezone preference | рџ”ө P0 | `users.timezone` field + dropdown in profile | No |
| Date/time format preference | рџџұ P2 | Display-only locale setting | No |
| MFA / TOTP (Google Authenticator) | рџџҰ P1 | TOTP setup flow + verify on login | No |
| Active session management (revoke devices) | рџџҰ P1 | Sessions table + revoke endpoint | No |
| Communication preferences | рџџұ P2 | Checkbox array mapping to notification DB | No |

**What to build for P0:**
- `PATCH /auth/me` в†’ update name, timezone
- Profile settings page in Next.js (`/settings/profile`)
- Store `timezone` column on `users` table

