| Industry / Vertical | рџџұ P2 | `tenants.industry` dropdown | No |
| Global timezone + currency | рџ”ө P0 | `tenants.timezone`, `tenants.currency` | No |
| Default UTM parameters | рџџҰ P1 | `tenants.utm_source/medium/campaign` + URL rewrite at send time | No |
| Parent/Child hierarchy (sub-accounts) | в¬› P3 | Complex. Needs `tenants.parent_tenant_id` relational tree | No |
| Identity tracking toggle | рџџҰ P1 | Boolean on tenant в†’ inject tracking pixels at send | No |
| Data sharing opt-out | рџџұ P2 | Boolean on tenant | No |

**Critical P0:** Dynamic physical address injection. Currently hardcoded in [email_sender.py](file:///Users/pamula/Desktop/email_engine/platform/worker/email_sender.py). Must be pulled from `tenants.business_address` before go-live.

