## Section 6 вЂ” Global Compliance & Data Privacy

| Feature | Priority | What To Build |
|---|---|---|
| Default opt-out type (one-click vs. preference center) | рџ”ө P0 | `tenants.unsubscribe_type` toggle + custom preference center URL |
| **GDPR: Data Portability export** (subscriber's full history) | рџџҰ P1 | Async export job: contacts + events + opens + clicks в†’ JSON/CSV |
| **GDPR: Right to Erasure** (delete a specific contact + all their data) | рџџҰ P1 | `DELETE /contacts/{id}/gdpr-erase` в†’ cascade all events, opens, clicks |
| GDPR: Data Retention Policy (auto-delete after X months) | рџџұ P2 | `tenants.retention_months` + scheduled cron job |
| CASL: Double opt-in toggle | рџџҰ P1 | `tenants.require_double_optin` вЂ” adds verification step to subscribe forms |
| CCPA: "Do Not Sell" link in footer | рџџұ P2 | Toggle + URL field в†’ injected to email footer |
| Data Processing Agreement (DPA) digital signing | рџџұ P2 | Display DPA, capture signature (checkbox + timestamp) |

