## Implementation Plan вЂ” Recommended Phase Order

```
Phase 6  в†’ Analytics + Tracking (NEXT - already planned)
Phase 7  в†’ Plan limits + Usage page (already planned)

[Account Settings вЂ” split into 3 sub-phases]

Phase 8A вЂ” Settings Core (2вЂ“3 weeks)
  вњ¦ Profile page (name, timezone)
  вњ¦ Organization page (company name, physical address в†’ fixes CAN-SPAM issue!)
  вњ¦ Team members (invite, assign roles, RBAC middleware)
  вњ¦ Billing/Usage page (plan + progress bars)
  вњ¦ Domain Verification page (SPF/DKIM/DMARC DNS record display + verify)

Phase 8B вЂ” Security & Compliance (2 weeks)
  вњ¦ Audit logs (table + settings UI)
  вњ¦ GDPR tools (data export, right-to-erasure endpoint)
  вњ¦ CASL double opt-in toggle
  вњ¦ Preference center page (/preferences?token=...)
  вњ¦ Session timeout configuration

Phase 8C вЂ” Developer Tools (2 weeks)
  вњ¦ API key management page
  вњ¦ Webhook configuration page
  вњ¦ DKIM key generation per-tenant
  вњ¦ Smart sending / fatigue management

Phase 9  в†’ Stripe payments (already planned)
```

