## Settings Navigation Structure (Frontend)

```
/settings
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ /settings/profile          вЂ” Name, email, timezone, avatar, MFA
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ /settings/organization     вЂ” Company name, address, industry, timezone
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ /settings/team             вЂ” Invite users, roles, remove members
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ /settings/domain           вЂ” Sending domain, SPF/DKIM/DMARC setup
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ /settings/billing          вЂ” Plan, usage bars, upgrade button
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ /settings/compliance       вЂ” GDPR tools, CASL toggle, data retention
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ /settings/audit-log        вЂ” Filterable action history
  в”њв”Ђв”Ђ /settings/api-keys         вЂ” Generate, view, revoke keys
  в””в”Ђв”Ђ /settings/webhooks         вЂ” Configure webhook URLs + event subscriptions
```

