## What NOT to Build Now (P3 вЂ” Document and Defer)

| Feature | Reason to Defer |
|---|---|
| SAML/SSO federation | Requires $5K+/year for SAML testing infrastructure. Only needed for enterprise sales. |
| BIMI logo in Gmail | Requires paid VMC certificate ($1,500+/year). Only after DMARC p=reject at 100%. |
| IP allowlist for login | Complex gateway layer. Not needed until SOC2 audit. |
| Parent/child sub-accounts | Major DB architecture change. Only needed for agency/franchise clients. |
| Microservices | Only needed after 5+ engineer team. Monolith handles 100K/day fine. |
| AI spam subject scanner | ML model. Phase 12 or later. |
